version 1.0 - April, 2005 - initial development complete

version 1.1 - Dec 2005 - add Nimbus 7 SMMR navigation position input
asap_int2.f     new routine to interpolate position, velocity data to get 
                navigation position for each line
cz_clean.c      change to add position error array
cz_dat_alloc.c  change to add position error array allocation
czl1merge.c     change to add version update and to fix size of num_used
cz_l1_read.c    change to add position error array reading
cz_mov_scn.c    change to add position error array management
day_to_ofile.c  new routine to construct orbit file name
fill_orb_dat.c  new routine to read proper orbit files and interpolate 
                it to the scan lines
l1czcs.c        change to add version update
l1czcs.h        change to include position error array to structure
l1czcs.mk       change to add new routines
rd_smmr_orb.c   new routine to read orbit data
read_crtt.c     change to call the orbit data read, interpolate routine, 
                fill_orb_dat
set_czcs_ctl_data.c  change to write the position error array
time_utl.c      new routine to perform some time conversions
time_utl.h      new include used by time_utl.c
